<plot>Profile of the Broadway team Alan Jay Lerner and Fritz Loewe, whose credits included the hit shows "Brigadoon", "Paint Your Wagon," "Gigi," "Camelot," and "My Fair Lady." Their story is told through interviews with the artists with whom they worked, and feature film and television excerpts.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?329556</url></doc>
